    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally optimized with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout, ensuring zero deflection under heavy cornering loads. The VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled for optimal cam timing. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car exhibits no paint imperfections or interior bolster wear. An absolute mechanical masterpiece for the enthusiast who demands factory-spec performance and structural perfection.",
