      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece, maintained to a standard that rivals a showroom floor model. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the color pop in any light. There are no chips, dings, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, with zero signs of wear on the bolsters or carpets. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive navigation, operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. This car has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and comes with a thick binder of service records. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
